  m_text: 'MC name can move by using WASD and can dash by pressing Spacebar but uses
    stamina


    You have 3 ability orbs that can be charged by killing enemies

    Press
    E to expand 1 orb in order to chop a tree and get a health pickup

    Press
    F to expand 2 orbs to push ennemies away

    Press Q to expand 3 orbs to close
    your eyes and make the monster go away'
